#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.13/guides/config-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "By default, Quarkus reads configuration properties from multiple sources (by descending ordinal):"
msgstr "默认情况下，Quarkus 会从多个来源（按降序）读取配置属性："

